extends ../_master

block scripts

block head
    title Register
block body
    h1 Register
    != messages()
    div.jumbotron.col-lg-10
        form.form-horizontal(action="/register", method="POST")
            fieldset
                section.form-group
                    label.col-lg-2.control-label(for='inputUsername') Username
                    div.col-lg-10
                        input#inputUsername.form-control(placeholder='Username', name='username', autocomplete='off', type='text', required)
                section.form-group
                    label.col-lg-2.control-label(for='inputFullName') Full Name
                    div.col-lg-10
                        input#inputFullName.form-control(placeholder='Full name', name='fullName', autocomplete='off', type='text', required)
                section.form-group
                    label.col-lg-2.control-label(for='inputEmail') Email
                    div.col-lg-10
                        input#inputEmail.form-control(placeholder='Email', name='email', autocomplete='off', type='text', required)
                section.form-group
                    label.col-lg-2.control-label(for='inputPassword') Password
                    div.col-lg-10
                        input#inputPassword.form-control(placeholder='Password', name='password', autocomplete='off', type='password', required)
                section.form-group
                    label.col-lg-2.control-label(for='inputPhone') Phone
                    div.col-lg-10
                        input#inputPhone.form-control(placeholder='Phone number', name='phone', autocomplete='off', type='tel', required)
                section.form-group
                    label.col-lg-2.control-label(for='inputAddress') Address
                    div.col-lg-10
                        input#inputAddress.form-control(placeholder="Address" name="address" autocomplete="off" type="address")
                        span.help-block
                            | We need your address in case of home visits.
                section.form-group(style='display:none;')
                    label.col-lg-2.control-label
                    div.col-lg-10
                        input.form-control(name='isAdmin', type='text', value='false')
                section.form-group
                    label.col-lg-2.control-label Gender
                    div.col-lg-10
                        div.radio.radio-inline(style='padding-left:0')
                            label
                                input#optionsRadios1(name='gender', value='male', checked='', type='radio')
                                | Male
                        div.radio.radio-inline
                            label
                                input#optionsRadios2(name='gender', value='female', type='radio')
                                | Female
                section.form-group
                    div.col-lg-10.col-lg-offset-2
                        div.checkbox
                            label
                                input(type='checkbox', name="acceptPolicy", required)
                                |  I have read and accept the 
                                span
                                    a#policy-link(href="#modal") privacy policy
                section.form-group
                    div.col-lg-10.col-lg-offset-2
                        button.btn.btn-default(type='reset') Cancel
                        button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit') Submit

    div#policy-modal.modal
        div.modal-dialog
            div.modal-content
                div.modal-header
                    button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='modal', aria-hidden='true') Ã—
                    h4.modal-title Privacy Policy
                div.modal-body
                    p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, mei assum fabellas an, in vix debet mandamus, solum verear definitiones no duo. Integre splendide dissentias nam in. Ea nam velit apeirian insolens, sanctus omittam scriptorem no pro. Vis amet wisi reprehendunt ad.
                div.modal-footer
                    button.btn.btn-default(type='button', data-dismiss='modal') Close

    script(src="/static/js/register.js")
